      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes an option for negotiating the use of robust header compression (ROHC) on IP datagrams transmitted over the Point- to-Point Protocol (PPP).  It defines extensions to the PPP Control Protocols for IPv4 and IPv6. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
